{"tid":638193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅鄰宅賣2.6億  折合實用呎價81,498元","createTime":"2018-04-22T13:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T15:00:56.000Z","uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"488f4baeed1b32bc4fe7824c377cddb3764bfb68","tid":638193,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:31:49.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅鄰宅2.6億沽<br />\n當中上下層加幅凌厲，今次推出的最貴單位22樓C室，實用面積338方呎，定價867.1萬元，較首張價單下層21樓C室定價810.3萬元，高出56.8萬元，加價約7%；最平單位11樓A室，實用面積173方呎，定價414.4萬元，較下層單位10樓A室定價372.3萬元貴逾42萬元，喪加逾一成。<br />\n另外，新地（016）旗下南區Shouson Peak，壽山村道19E號洋房，以約2.62億元標售沽出，實用面積3,218方呎，折合實用呎價81,498元。<br />\n資料顯示，歌星陳奕迅2013年以太太徐濠縈名義，以逾2.31億元購入毗鄰大屋，實用面積3,238方呎，成交呎價71,426元，5年升幅近14.1%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180422/20369267?_ga=2.184807209.1207529650.1524325724-1387409261.1504544975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369267%3F_ga%3D2.184807209.1207529650.1524325724-1387409261.1504544975&d=nBFEAOULz8l72pXpn6iQDWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d37b06c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369267%3F_ga%3D2.184807209.1207529650.1524325724-1387409261.1504544975&h=8e613fb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180422/20369267?_ga=2.184807209.1207529650.1524325724-1387409261.1504544975</a>"},{"pid":"c643f301967cdac68113e15cf91776a94429ea09","tid":638193,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"5年升14%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94003a26ed5b20396bf21a2252bdd544384bdf0","tid":638193,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:35:38.000Z","msg":"獨立屋有咩好講<br />\n依啲成交量低就話咩就咩㗎啦"},{"pid":"994c51603000b3fa8b9b8874bed860df3750d39e","tid":638193,"ui